{"tid":595831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅馬尼亞男被判「死亡」15年 親身出庭申請「翻生」失敗不得上訴","createTime":"2018-03-17T05:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T14:50:46.000Z","uid":3393,"like":202,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"c35569d3810c6fd391d4ab0985b384f8be118f95","tid":595831,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:21:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/169141/thumbnail/2c8a7ffbc77c5beaae836f3e22a7faf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F169141%2Fthumbnail%2F2c8a7ffbc77c5beaae836f3e22a7faf3.jpg&h=b32adb30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅馬尼亞最近發生一宗奇怪案件，當地法院裁定一名63歲男子「死亡」，但這名男子活生生的在庭上證明自己未死。羅馬尼亞一名已婚男子早年到土耳其當廚師，但之後他沒和家人聯繫，妻子尋夫不得，唯有幫他申領死亡證。男子今年回到羅馬尼亞，卻發現自己「已死」，他向法庭申請推翻裁決卻敗訴，「翻生」失敗的他無奈道：「我已經正式死了，儘管我還活着。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1284136/xlarge/2f8a07cc3d5daa928404cd27168fc161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1284136%2Fxlarge%2F2f8a07cc3d5daa928404cd27168fc161.jpg&h=d44a54d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1284139/xlarge/765c4fb165a3800dacc1d4bef170fd48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1284139%2Fxlarge%2F765c4fb165a3800dacc1d4bef170fd48.jpg&h=72ffe568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年63歲的維魯（Reliu）1992年時遠赴土耳其當廚師賺錢，之後音訊全無。他的妻子尋夫不果唯有幫他申請死亡證，當時她在法院上稱相信丈夫已在地震中死亡，法院裁定維魯「已死」。維魯相信妻子這樣做的目的，是方便自己取消婚約並重新結婚。他解釋指，1995年時自己曾經回國，但發現妻子已經紅杏出牆，1999年他決定返回土耳其，過好一點的生活。<br />\n<br />\n今年初，土耳其當局發現逾期居留，將他遣返回羅馬尼亞。維魯原打算回國更新護照再返回土耳其，但他抵達時被移民局官員拘留，指他在2003年已經「去世」，如果他不是被遣返，可能一世也不知自己在祖國「已死」。他在機上被盤問了足足6小時，還要進行不同測試，安檢人員才相信他是維魯本人。<br />\n<br />\n維魯希望法院讓自己「翻生」，但法庭認為他過了上訴期限，判他敗訴，而且判決是取終裁決，他不能再上訴。維魯在庭外嘆道：「我沒有收入，而且因為我被判死亡，我甚麼都不能做。」維魯原本打算回土耳其開一間小公司渡過餘生，但他現在只能活於法律的灰色地帶。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/熱話/169141/羅馬尼亞男被判-死亡-15年-親身出庭申請-翻生-失敗不得上訴\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F169141%2F%E7%BE%85%E9%A6%AC%E5%B0%BC%E4%BA%9E%E7%94%B7%E8%A2%AB%E5%88%A4-%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1-15%E5%B9%B4-%E8%A6%AA%E8%BA%AB%E5%87%BA%E5%BA%AD%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E7%BF%BB%E7%94%9F-%E5%A4%B1%E6%95%97%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4&d=fZM7N6QrlwatQABWD2VYMy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=1388cf11\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/熱話/169141/羅馬尼亞男被判-死亡-15年-親身出庭申請-翻生-失敗不得上訴</a>"},{"pid":"a5e0be606149fac7a06cc20e3d2a7f6b24246c7e","tid":595831,"uid":69794,"like":315,"dislike":5,"score":310,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://jackydahlhaus.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/i-see-dead-people.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjackydahlhaus.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F06%2Fi-see-dead-people.jpg&h=73152739&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d855417b2e7e6e44f871ca0fc1a7287a08c66c7e","tid":595831,"uid":55386,"like":15,"dislike":29,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"明日香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8613150902370ca46283cee8df92b013373b79a2","tid":595831,"uid":170974,"like":221,"dislike":2,"score":219,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"比人派帽都算 連搵個錢都無得<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254c3587543f56aa05787800977775ee3a04b28a","tid":595831,"uid":51720,"like":74,"dislike":5,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:28:10.000Z","msg":"《致命復活》重現 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26fa3e339a9a18ef21536936cfeb6feac4b6ef0","tid":595831,"uid":3393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc5e726a7ad110732df77047f37608742d64768","tid":595831